Package: clawix
Version: __VERSION__
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: Clawix <support@clawix.com>
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0, libgtk-3-0, libayatana-appindicator3-1, libssl3, avahi-daemon, libnotify4
Recommends: wtype | xdotool, wl-clipboard | xclip
Suggests: nodejs, libvulkan1
Homepage: https://clawix.com
Description: Clawix desktop companion for Linux
 Clawix pairs with your iPhone over a local WebSocket bridge, runs
 dictation locally with whisper.cpp, and orchestrates AI workflows
 through the same engine that powers the macOS and iOS apps.
